text: Sara Jean Underwood (born March 26, 1984) is an American nude model, television host and actress. She was chosen as Playmate of the Month for the July 2006 issue of Playboy Magazine and later became Playmate of the Year in 2007. she was best known for being on G4’s Attack of the Show! from 2010 until 2013 when she was the anchor for one of the AOTS segments, “ The Feed “. She was born on March 26, 1984 in Portland, Oregon. Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Adult models Category:Glamour models Category:American models
